## Write a program to convert minutes to weeks

1 week = 7 days = 168 hours = 10080 minutes

```txt
Input  : 50400
Output : 5
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="convert-minutes-to-weeks" >

```cpp
#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;

int main()
{
    long long int mins, weeks;
    cin>>mins;

    // 1 week = 7 days = 168 hours = 10080 minutes
    weeks=mins/10080;
    cout<<weeks;

}
```

```java
import java.util.*;
import java.lang.*;

